addCoachToTeam(int, int) - Method in class Controller.SysData
This method adds an existing coach to an existing team of the JavaLeague only if all the parameters are valid and the both coach & team already exist in the system IMPORTANT: If the given coach already belongs to another team, transfer the coach to the given team.

addCustomerToMatch(String, int) - Method in class Controller.SysData
This method adds an existing customer to an existing match of the JavaLeague only if all the parameters are valid and both customer & match already exist in the system VERY IMPORTANT: Customer must be added to all the relevant arrays, Don't forget to roll-back :)
